Package org.opencastproject.workflow.conditionparser.antlr

Interface WorkflowConditionListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
WorkflowConditionBaseListener
public interface WorkflowConditionListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by WorkflowConditionParser.
